<span id="freeTextContainer8854027528909597476">This is one of those books where you are one person prior to reading it, and another person once you’ve finished reading it. The kind of book that crawls inside you and stays there. Is there anything more important than doing the inner &amp; outer work needed to live in right community on this planet? I don’t think so. Read this book. We all need you to.<br/><br/>(Note: not as radical as I’d like / some cop apologizing and fat phobia. Gave it 5 stars because I want folks to read it but pls note those disclaim</span>
