<span id="freeTextContainer8839763332895670007"><strong>One of the most necessary books written on healing racism!</strong><br/><br/>The framework Resmaa has laid out in this book is the best I have seen in relation to healing historical trauma, retention trauma and acute race based trauma. Anyone born in America or planning to live here should have this book right next to their first aid kit! Hotep!</span>

