      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3177116648" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10531718186387526191">I rarely say things are a &quot;must-read,&quot; but this really is. For anyone invested in anti-racism, for anyone who wants to know how we will truly heal from the legacy (&amp; contemporary work of) white supremacy, please read this. </span>
  <span id="freeText10531718186387526191" style="display:none">I rarely say things are a "must-read," but this really is. For anyone invested in anti-racism, for anyone who wants to know how we will truly heal from the legacy (&amp; contemporary work of) white supremacy, please read this. </span>
  <a data-text-id="10531718186387526191" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

